  "title": "CAD Drafter (Construction) [Woodlands | 5.5 days | up to $3500] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>CAD Drafter (Construction Industry)</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Location: Woodland</strong></li><li><strong>Salary: $3000 - $3500</strong></li><li><strong>Working Hours: 5.5 Days | 830am – 530pm [Mon to Fri] | 830am – 1230pm [Sat]</strong></li></ul><p><u><strong>Company Overview</strong></u></p><p>The Company is a well‑established construction and engineering company with a strong presence in both local and international markets. Recognized for the company’s commitment to quality, safety, and innovation, the company delivers effective solutions across a wide range of projects and continue to build trusted partnerships with clients worldwide.<br /><br /><u><strong>Responsibility</strong></u></p><ul><li>Prepare 2D and 3D drawings based on specifications, sketches, and engineering components.</li><li>Revise and update drawings as directed by engineers or project managers.</li><li>Interpret technical drawings, plans, and specifications accurately.</li><li>Ensure all drawings comply with company standards and project requirements.</li><li>Maintain organized records of drawings, files, and revisions.</li><li>Collaborate closely with engineers, architects, and other stakeholders to support project delivery.</li><li>Conduct site visits and assist with measurements when required.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li><strong>Diploma in Architectural/Civil & Structural </strong>or equivalent and recognized by relevant authority</li><li><strong>Minimum 2 years’ experience in AutoCAD drafting</strong></li><li>Proficient in Revit/ Solid works/ Sketchup is an added advantage</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
